Reference list:

-----
Spring's official reference
http://docs.spring.io/spring-data/solr/docs/1.5.0.RELEASE/reference/html/

-----
An author of Spring Data Solr's example
https://github.com/christophstrobl/spring-data-solr-showcase/ (there's an associated YouTube video, but shows no more
 than this example)

-----
DZone article
https://dzone.com/articles/getting-started-spring-data

-----
Another example, nice to see its tests
https://github.com/mscharhag/Spring-data-solr-example/blob/master/src/test/java/com/mscharhag/solr/repository/BookRepositoryTests.java

-----
Relatively old, but quite comprehensive example of getting started
http://www.petrikainulainen.net/programming/solr/spring-data-solr-tutorial-configuration/

-----
Custom REST message converters:
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/30757981/rest-custom-http-message-converter-spring-boot-1-2-3
